        "geocode_query": "900 143rd Ave, San Leandro",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 900 143rd Ave, San Leandro, CA 94578 Welcome home to Parkside Commons! Our apartments are located near the Lower Bal neighborhood of San Leandro. Choose from our 1 or 2 bedroom apartments that are complete with everything that you need to feel right at home. Our property is located within minutes of major highways, thoroughfares, public transit, and world-class sporting and entertainment events. Parkside Commons is a gated community that adds convenience and comfort to your everyday life. Stay active in our 24-hour fitness center, or dive into our swimming pool. Our community features the ideal combination of personal and community amenities that will enhance your daily routine, including private balconies, large bedrooms, and walk-in closets. Our floor plans range from 1 bedroom apartments to 2 bedroom apartments and 2 bedroom townhomes with high-quality features and enhanced finishes. Each floor plan includes a fully equipped kitchen, ample storage, large bedrooms, and more. Discover our San Leandro apartments and come home to better living at Parkside Commons! Apartment Features: Built-In Microwave LARGE BEDROOMS STORAGE SPACE DISHWASHER WINDOW COVERINGS PRIVATE BALCONIES/PATIOS GARBAGE DISPOSAL CEILING FANS Community Features: Swimming Pool & Jacuzzi Professional Landscaping State-of-the-Art Fitness Center Playground Controlled Access Entry Building Near public transit Assigned covered parking & Guest Parking Online Rental Payment Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livehmaprop.com/ajch7zoa/parkside-commons Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
