        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Charming 2 bedroom,2 bathroom apartment located in a desirable Belmont neighborhood. This spacious home features hardwood floors throughout, a functional fireplace, a separate dining room, and a large bedroom. The kitchen includes a gas range, dishwasher, and refrigerator, with the added convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer. Step outside to enjoy a large private yard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, parks, and major commuter routes. Rent: *$1720/month*. Contact today to schedule a viewing. Interested renters can message their phone number anytime.",
