        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to Walnut Hill Located in Downtown's sought-after art district and close to Bart, Walnut Hill offers a variety of apartment home sizes to suit your household. With award-winning management, sizeable patios and decks, open floor plans, dual pane windows and sliding doors, modern fixtures, and sunny kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Walnut Hill will be the downtown Walnut Creek apartments you'll be proud to call 'home'. Contact us today and schedule a tour with our leasing team to learn more about our community. Apartment Features: Ceramic Cooktop Oversized Patio or Deck Space Modern Lighting Washer and Dryer Updated Kitchen Cabinetry Stainless-Steel Dishwasher Stainless-Steel Refrigerator Quartz Countertops Community Features: Laundry Facilities Minutes From Major Employers & Educational Institutions Close to Shopping, Dining & Entertainment Pet-Friendly Community Outdoor Barbecue Smoke Pit Clubhouse Poolside Sundeck & Lounge Areas Swimming Pool Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livefpi.com/6ylvxaqv/walnut-hill *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up-to-date information!",
