        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 777 Shell Boulevard, Foster City, CA 94404 Come home to an oasis where you can savor gentle breezes under the warmth of the sun. Sand Cove offers waterfront living with spacious 1 and 2 bedroom floor plans, complete with beautifully appointed kitchens. large private patios and balconies offering stunning bay views, walk-in closets, and hardwood floors. Amenities Include: Plush carpets Granite countertops Community gas grill/BBQ area Beach volleyball and bocce ball courts Non-smoking community Professional on-site maintenance Outdoor pool and firepit lounge with cushy seating Custom cabinetry with ample cabinet space Wood plank style flooring in living areas Walk-in closets Charming green space and beautiful courtyard views Ceiling fans in living areas Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewres.com/pvrbneye/sand-cove *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up-to-date information!",
