        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 26409 Gading Rd, Hayward, CA 94544 Our team is ready to help you find your new apartment from wherever you are. If you're interested in our affordable two-, three- or four-bedroom homes, call or email our leasing team so that we may provide you with more information about availability and income qualifications for these apartment homes. Income limits are based on median income and vary by floor plan type. Income Limits (80% AMI)1 Person: $101,5202 Person: $116,0003 Person: $130,5604 Person: $145,0405 Person: $156,640 A well-designed community gives your life that extra element of appeal. No matter what your day-to-day looks like, start and end it in a Hayward community with all the perks you’d hope for. Whether it’s productive days, restful evenings, or access to an incredible neighborhood, find it all at Townhomes on Gading – and with online rental payments and close proximity to parks, life here looks even better. Amenities Include: Private Patio Online Rental Payments Abundant Closet Space Dishwasher Playground Mature Landscape Large Windows Laundry Facilities Resident Community Room Close Proximity to Parks Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewres.com/7s2kj6le/townhomes-at-gading *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up-to-date information!",
