        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 100 Boyd Road, Pleasant Hill, CA 94523 Unique and Inspiring Pleasant Hill Apartments Presenting an exciting multi-million-dollar renovation, 100 Boyd provides cutting-edge amenities designed to elevate your standard of living, from a state-of-the-art fitness center to a modern community room. A full landscape revamp offers a vibrant atmosphere that encourages rest and relaxation, and our newly renovated Pleasant Hill apartments deliver the true comfort of home. 100 Boyd additionally boasts the perfect location right in the heart of downtown. The City of Pleasant Hill is a major suburb that was included on 24/7 Wall Street's list of \"America's 50 Best Cities to Live In.\" Close by, you'll find a charming mix of unique shops, services and restaurants and best of all, getting around is easy with the BART Station just one mile away and our close proximity to the 680 Freeway. Come in today so you can have your pick of one of our beautifully renovated one bedroom apartment homes. Features Include: Walk-In Closet Ceiling Fan Clubhouse Fitness Center Cable Ready Fully Equipped Kitchen Business Center BBQ Area Air Conditioning Laundry Facility Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livegkmanagement.com/ona5h5yb/100-boyd Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up to date information.",
