        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post All utilities are included Pet Friendly building, quiet 2nd floor apartment in the Pill Hill/Uptown neighborhood. The unit has one bedroom and one full bathroom with tub and shower, stove and refrigerator and in-unit laundry room off the kitchen with washer and dryer. The apartment also has a large sunny deck off the Living Room French Doors. It's a short walk to the MacArthur BART and 19th Street BART stations. and short walking distance Lake Merritt, Sprouts, Whole Foods and 2 blocks from Oakland's monthly First Fridays. All utilities are included Lease Duration: 1 Year Total move in is the first and last months rent. Proof of Employment. Positive rental history with no evictions. Please provide a current credit report with rental application.",
