        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 26379 Whitman Street, Hayward, CA 94544 Let lush gardens and tranquil fountains welcome you home to Whitman Green, a comfortable apartment community conveniently located in Hayward. Inside our pet-friendly one, two, and three bedroom floor plans, an elevated living experience awaits you. Enjoy the convenience of your home’s fully equipped kitchen, spacious living area, and large walk-in closets. Discover additional space to relax on a private patio or balcony or beside a cozy fireplace, available in select models. Contact a friendly staff member at Whitman Green to tour our apartments today. Amenities Include: Energy efficient double paned windows Receiving Shared garages Club House Patios Energy efficient fixtures and appliances Dishwasher included Abundance natural light Covered parking Wood plank inspired flooring Plush carpets Some units have fireplaces Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewres.com/e3vwaqnc/whitman-green *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up-to-date information!",
