        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 44 Harder Road, Hayward, CA 94544 The Woodlark is a small apartment community well located near highways 880 and 92. Our recently renovated apartment homes feature stainless steel appliances, stone countertops, hardwood-like flooring, two-tone paint, and modern finishes. All of our 1 & 2 -bedroom residences include a private patio or balcony, covered parking, and plenty of storage space. The community is well landscaped, features a refreshing swimming pool, has on-site laundry care facilities, and gated parking areas. Amenities Include: Entry closet Pet friendly Plush carpets Non-smoking community Quartz countertops Close proximity to local shops Easy to clean designer cabinetry Elevator building Fireplace AT&T u-verse fiber internet Lush landscaping Beautiful courtyard views Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewres.com/tt3qcitm/woodlark *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit. Contact us today for the most up-to-date information!",
