        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Stunning, Sun-Drenched Full-Floor Flat in One of SF's Most Coveted Neighborhoods! Welcome to 20 Belvedere a spectacular 6-room flat where timeless period charm meets sophisticated modern living. This breathtaking residence features 2 expansive, private bedrooms and jaw-dropping light-filled public rooms that will leave you speechless from the moment you walk in. Entertain in style in the dramatic west-facing living room, anchored by a gorgeous decorative fireplace, or gather around the table in the sublime dining room a true showstopper with its soaring beamed ceiling and stunning period built-ins. The beautifully updated kitchen dazzles with rich custom wood cabinetry and crisp quartz counters, blending form and function seamlessly. Interested renters can message their phone number anytime.",
