        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Villa Alvarado Apartments! Pet-friendly studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and townhouse apartments in San Pablo, CA. Here you are conveniently close to I-80, shopping & BART. You'll enjoy our beautiful garden style landscaping with lovely courtyard views! We offer our residents reserved covered parking with extra parking available. We are a gated community featuring a sparkling blue pool, off-leash dog park, and 6 convenient laundry care centers. Our management is friendly, professional and on-site! Maintenance is available 24-hours and is also on-site. Location, location location! We are a great commute location to San Francisco, located near Doctor’s Medical Center, public transportation, and major shops & stores. You'll love it here! This apartment features: REMODELED  2-story townhouse w/ patio Enjoy courtyard view! Modern finishes Desired gas heat & cooking Quartz countertops & Stainless appliances Spacious living room Large patio Ceilings fans in bedrooms & dining room Plenty of storage includes linen closet, 2 large storage closets Generous closets in each bedroom, one with walk-in closet Elegant wood-style flooring throughout 1st floor Near on-site laundry facility Assigned parking Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan. Come Visit us! Villa Alvarado 1330 Contra Costa Ave San Pablo, CA 94806 https://livecreativejuices.com/zpfnm6wo/villa-alvarado Contact us today to schedule a tour! Call show contact info Office Hours Tuesday – Friday 9:00am – 6:00pm Saturday 9:00am – 2:00pm Closed on Sunday & Monday Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.",
